==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Granny
<hw>Gran"ny</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A grandmother; a
grandam; familiarly, an old woman.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>Granny's bend</b></col>, <it>or</it>
<col><b>Granny's knot</b></col></mcol> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>, <cd>a kind of
insecure knot or hitch; a reef knot crossed the wrong way.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Granolithic</ent>⟦br⟧
